                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <br>
                        <div>
                            <h2>Do other Companies use cookies in connection with The Hydraulisc Network Products?</h2>
                            <p>Yes, third-party companies may use cookies regarding information associated with your data and/or activities on or across The Hydraulisc Network Products to provide certain features and improve services for you. To understand how third parties use cookies, please review their policies.</p>
                        </div>
                        <br>
                        <div>
                            <h2>How can you control your information?</h2>
                            <p>You can control how we use data to show you ads and more by using the tools described below.</p>
